biogHist.list:
This archival collection includes:


Records about the financial and administrative running of Toolgan Bale, Illawong, Belmont Helpers Guild, and the Forest Guild;

Records in alphabetical order by name of estate titles 'Bequest Files'; 

Records in alphabetical order by name of people who experienced care titled 'Files Regarding English Discharges - Boys'; and 

Records in alphabetical order by name of people who experienced care titled 'Girls'.
